Mod that will make a custom page so people can leave comments for eachother.

It will add a link in the profile page where all the comments for the person are showed.
In the comment page people can add comments.

The mod has custom instll/uninstall script so you don't have to browse and edit the files.

The mod is in very earle stage and in the future it will be updated.

Demo:
https://imgur.com/a/SN4Ww5B
